snippet.title: UFL™ Developer Diary Series #2 | Cutscenes
snippet.description: The second episode of #UFLDevDiaries covers our vision & process of creating in-game cutscenes. You might have seen it during our live event, yet it may serve as a good recap while our third episode is in production!
